text: [Eamonn Holmes](/presenters/eamonn-holmes/) [Nigel Farage](/presenters/nigel-farage/) [Isabel Webster](/presenters/isabel-webster/) [Jacob Rees-Mogg](/presenters/jacob-rees-mogg/) [Michelle Dewberry](/presenters/michelle-dewberry/) [Dan Wootton](/presenters/dan-wootton/) [Patrick Christys](/presenters/patrick-christys/) [Nana Akua](/presenters/nana-akua/) [Stephen Dixon](/presenters/stephen-dixon/) [Anne Diamond](/presenters/anne-diamond/) [Andrew Pierce](/presenters/andrew-pierce/) [Beverley Turner](/presenters/beverley-turner/) [Mark Longhurst](/presenters/mark-longhurst/) [Mark Dolan](/presenters/mark-dolan/) [Camilla Tominey](/presenters/camilla-tominey/) [Michael Portillo](/presenters/michael-portillo/) [Gloria De Piero](/presenters/gloria-de-piero/) [Neil Oliver](/presenters/neil-oliver/) [Tom Harwood](/presenters/tom-harwood/) [Andrew Doyle](/presenters/andrew-doyle/) [Philip Davies](/presenters/philip-davies/) [Emily Carver](/presenters/emily-carver/) [Simon Evans](/presenters/simon-evans/) [Arlene Foster](/presenters/arlene-foster/) [Olivia Utley](/presenters/olivia-utley/) [Liam Halligan](/presenters/liam-halligan/) [Ellie Costello](/presenters/ellie-costello/) [Darren Grimes](/presenters/darren-grimes/) [Mark White](/presenters/mark-white/) [Cameron Walker](/presenters/cameron-walker/) Published: 25/01/2024- 20:51 US President Joe Biden has been slammed by the Chair of Republicans Overseas UK, as the battle between the Biden administration and the Governor of Texas continues. Earlier this month, Texan Governor Greg Abbott ordered a razor wire to be installed on the US-Mexico border, amid soaring levels of illegal migrant crossings.
